cx.description: Specifies the x coordinate of the center of a circle

cy.description: Specifies the y coordinate of the center of a circle

d.description: Defines a path to be drawn

fill.description: Specifies the fill color of a graphic

height.description: Specifies the height of an element

href.description: Specifies the URL of the linked resource

opacity.description: Specifies the opacity of an element

r.description: Specifies the radius of a circle

stroke.description: Specifies the stroke color of a graphic

stroke-width.description: Specifies the width of the stroke

viewBox.description: Defines the position and size of the viewport

width.description: Specifies the width of an element

x.description: Specifies the x coordinate of an element

y.description: Specifies the y coordinate of an element

z.description: Specifies the position of the element along the z-axis

class.description: Specifies one or more classnames for an element

id.description: Specifies a unique ID for an element

mask.description: Specifies a mask for an element

preserveAspectRatio.description: Defines how an element's viewBox will be scaled and positioned

style.description: Specifies an inline style for an element

text-anchor.description: Specifies the horizontal alignment of text

text-decoration.description: Specifies the decoration added to text

viewTarget.description: Specifies the target of a hyperlink in a 'view' element

visibility.description: Specifies whether or not an element is visible
